<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_247_r1l6"> <expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her <expan>Lantrıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Vns hat fürgelegt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_247_r1l5">Es ıſt für vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> F . Cʒeſel vnſer <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> / vnd hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l7">vns geweıſet einen kündbrief / als Jr Jm geſant habt von eins <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l8">genant <expan cert="unknown">B</expan> . walch / das vns ſelcʒeim vnd fremde nymt / vvan wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l9">noch die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> auf </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_247_line_1576584675061_3454">für </ab></add> ewr gerichte nicht gehören/ vnd auch nye </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l10">darauf geantwurt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . So ſein vvir auch von Römiſchen <expan>keyſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l11">vnd künigen gefreyet / . daʒ wir noch die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / auf dhein Gerıcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l12">anderſwo nyndert geladen noch beklagt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> ſüllen / dann / vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l13">des Reiches <expan>Richt<ex>er</ex></expan> hie cʒü <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / . <expan>Dar<ex>vmb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / . daʒ Jr ſölicher </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l14">klage vor <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> Gerichte gen <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nicht geſtatten / vnd das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l15">abtün wöllet / . vnd vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſſet / bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l16"><expan>freyheit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd als das von <expan>alt<ex>er</ex></expan> her <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt / . Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l17">vnd het <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> walch cʒü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> ıht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l18"><expan>Dar<ex>vmb</ex></expan> vvöllen vvir Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheinbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> vollen gewalt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l19"><expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogen<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſlewnig<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen / vor des Reiches <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l20">hie cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / vvenn wir des ermant <expan>werd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / ſo derſelb vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l21"><expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ıſt / . vnd laʒʒet vns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l22"><expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vvıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> bey <expan>dıſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_247" id="123r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>De<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, vesten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conrat<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Thaning<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> in
                        dem Kleggöw</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                            <add>es ist für uns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<expan cert="unknown">F<ex>ritz</ex></expan> Czesel, unser
                                <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan>, und hat uns geweiset einen
                        kündbrief, als ir im gesant habt von eins <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        genant <expan>B<ex>erthold</ex></expan> Walch, das uns selczeim und fremde
                        nymt, wan wir noch die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>für</add> ewr gerichte nicht gehören und auch nye darauf geantwurt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. So sein wir auch von römischen
                                <expan>keys<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und künigen gefreyet, daz wir noch
                        die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auf dhein gericht anderswo nyndert
                        geladen noch beklagt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> süllen dann vor des
                        reiches <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> hie czü
                            <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir sölicher klage vor
                                <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> gerichte gen
                            <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nicht gestatten und das abtün wöllet, und uns
                        und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lasset bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>freyheit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und als das von
                            <expan>alt<ex>er</ex></expan> her <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Walch czü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> iht
                            <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
                        wöllen wir im <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        vollen gewalt <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogen<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen vor des reiches
                                <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> hie czü
                            <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>werd<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so derselb unser
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ist. Und lazzet uns des
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
